{"tha-ap441:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap441:0.2":"Ekaviharivagga ","tha-ap441:0.3":"Ambapindiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap441:1.1":"“Hatthiraja tada asim, ","tha-ap441:1.2":"isadanto urulhava; ","tha-ap441:1.3":"Vicaranto braharanne, ","tha-ap441:1.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap441:2.1":"Ambapindam gahetvana, ","tha-ap441:2.2":"adasim satthuno aham; ","tha-ap441:2.3":"Patigganhi mahaviro, ","tha-ap441:2.4":"siddhattho lokanayako. ","tha-ap441:3.1":"Mama nijjhayamanassa, ","tha-ap441:3.2":"paribhunji tada jino; ","tha-ap441:3.3":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap441:3.4":"tusitam upapajjaham. ","tha-ap441:4.1":"Tato aham cavitvana, ","tha-ap441:4.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap441:4.3":"Eteneva upayena, ","tha-ap441:4.4":"anubhutvana sampada. ","tha-ap441:5.1":"Padhanapahitattoham, ","tha-ap441:5.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap441:5.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap441:5.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap441:6.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap441:6.2":"yam phalamadadim tada; ","tha-ap441:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap441:6.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap441:7.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap441:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap441:7.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap441:8.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap441:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap441:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap441:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap441:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap441:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap441:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ambapindiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap441:11.1":"Ambapindiyattherassapadanam navamam. "}